longBusinessSummary: Sienna Resources Inc. engages in the identification, acquisition, and exploration of mineral properties in Canada, Finland, Norway, and the United States. It primarily explores for platinum, palladium, and lithium deposits. The company also holds an option to acquire a 100% interest in the Elko lithium project that covers an area of 1200 contiguous acres in Elko County, Nevada. The company was formerly known as Habanero Resources Inc. and changed its name to Sienna Resources Inc. in January 2014. Sienna Resources Inc. was incorporated in 1983 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
